com.reactivecascade.i

Interface ICancellable.State

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAsyncOrigin
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ICancellable.StateCancelled, ICancellable.StateError
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractAltFuture.AbstractState, AbstractAltFuture.AltFutureStateCancelled, AbstractAltFuture.AltFutureStateError
    Enclosing interface:
    ICancellable

    public static interface ICancellable.State
extends IAsyncOrigin
    An internal-use interface made public to facilitate mixing in alternate implementations.

    The Reactive Cascade library exposes thread-safe atomic internal states for extension, default implementation replacement and transparency during debugging. Most application developers will not need to use this interface directly.
